WEBVTT

00:00:21.229 --> 00:00:22.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Who is that?

00:00:22.854 --> 00:00:25.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Does she go to our school?

00:00:34.729 --> 00:00:36.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Good morning, everyone.

00:00:36.854 --> 00:00:38.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We have a new classmate.

00:00:38.854 --> 00:00:41.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Her name is Priya, from India.

00:00:41.479 --> 00:00:42.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
She’s from where?

00:00:42.645 --> 00:00:43.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I dunno.

00:00:43.645 --> 00:00:44.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’ve never heard of it.

00:00:44.854 --> 00:00:48.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
OK, so let’s work in pairs again.

00:00:48.770 --> 00:00:51.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Who needs a partner
and can team up with Priya?

00:00:55.520 --> 00:00:57.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hey, Sophia.

00:00:57.395 --> 00:00:59.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’re a team, right?

00:01:01.187 --> 00:01:03.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Um, yeah. OK.

00:01:03.770 --> 00:01:05.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
OK, great!

00:01:05.104 --> 00:01:07.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So for the first page,

00:01:07.104 --> 00:01:09.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m thinking we can do this and then that.

00:01:13.187 --> 00:01:15.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is taken.

00:01:27.145 --> 00:01:31.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So, what did Jesus teach us to do to be

00:01:31.312 --> 00:01:33.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a real neighbor like the Samaritan?

00:01:33.562 --> 00:01:36.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Sophia?

00:01:36.062 --> 00:01:38.687 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He taught us to show love and kindness

00:01:38.687 --> 00:01:40.687 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
when somebody needs help.

00:01:43.187 --> 00:01:45.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Priya!

00:01:46.145 --> 00:01:48.354 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Over here!

00:01:51.479 --> 00:01:53.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hi! I’m Sophia.

00:01:53.312 --> 00:01:54.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hello.

00:01:54.854 --> 00:01:56.937 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I like your outfit.

00:01:56.937 --> 00:01:58.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Where did you get it?

00:01:58.437 --> 00:02:00.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My mom made it.

00:02:00.062 --> 00:02:02.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s from my country.

00:02:02.062 --> 00:02:04.270 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They call it a <i>shalwar kameez.</i>

00:02:04.270 --> 00:02:06.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This one is my favorite color.

00:02:06.479 --> 00:02:07.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What’s it like where you lived?

